1. you are not allowed to redistribute exact copies, except from seeding the official torrents

2. you are not allowed to distribute modified versions and any contributions to the source grants all rights to the licensee

3. software is free of any form of monetization, except from donations
3.1 if the licensee sells physical goods related to the project, they need to provide a complete financial report and salaries between employees can't exceed a ratio greater than 1:5

4. if the licensee breaks rule 3.x, a legal case should filled and within a year of no resolution, the software belongs to the first complainant, under this same license